2.  Specific Deliverables 
14.  Specific deliverables for the communication specialists are 
(i)  revamping the NPT project website specifications;  
(ii)  developing a project brief, questions and answers, talking points, basic public 
presentation, newsletter articles (internal and external), and storyline on NPT’s 
plans;  
(iii)  with the NPT communications officer, refining the stakeholder mapping; 
(iv)  developing a contacts database with email newsletter ability; 
(v)  creating a photo and video footage database; 
(vi)  developing a project outreach calendar;  
(vii)  developing a program of regular briefings with key constituencies inside and 
outside ADB; and 
(viii)  providing  guidance  to  NPT’s  communications  team  on  developing  their 
communications  department  by  providing  terms  of  reference  and  budget  for 
hiring of communications professionals, strategies to improve public image and 
reputation, improve communications support, websites, etc.
